    57→ * - 3-4: Mild frustration, dissatisfaction
    58→ * - 5: Neutral (logged as baseline for feature requests)
    59→ * - 6-7: Satisfaction, approval
    60→ * - 8-9: Strong approval, impressed
    61→ * - 10: Extraordinary enthusiasm
